composed of stones weighing
in excess of 30 tons that

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:48.990 align:middle line:90%
defy our human understanding.

00:08:48.990 --> 00:08:53.220 align:middle line:84%
If civilization only happened
roughly 5,000 to 6,000 years

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:56.340 align:middle line:84%
ago, then who built these
foundational wonders

00:08:56.340 --> 00:08:59.940 align:middle line:84%
in prediluvian times that
were designed to survive

00:08:59.940 --> 00:09:01.500 align:middle line:90%
the end of the world?

00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:03.750 align:middle line:84%
And what were those
beings who inhabited

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:06.270 align:middle line:84%
the Earth long before
the flood trying

00:09:06.270 --> 00:09:10.240 align:middle line:84%
to tell us about our
connection to the cosmos?

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:14.410 align:middle line:84%
We turn to science for answers
to help unravel the mystery.

00:09:14.410 --> 00:09:18.250 align:middle line:84%
But when we look below the
surface, the laws of physics

00:09:18.250 --> 00:09:21.550 align:middle line:84%
appear to have been mastered
long before humanity

00:09:21.550 --> 00:09:24.400 align:middle line:90%
began to figure them out.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:27.760 align:middle line:10%
- Science is a living
body of information.

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:28.790 align:middle line:10%
It's not static.

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:30.370 align:middle line:10%
It's not fixed.

00:09:30.370 --> 00:09:33.100 align:middle line:10%
It's designed to be
constantly updated.

00:09:33.100 --> 00:09:35.560 align:middle line:10%
When new discoveries
come to light,

00:09:35.560 --> 00:09:38.020 align:middle line:10%
we've got to incorporate
those discoveries

00:09:38.020 --> 00:09:40.480 align:middle line:10%
into the pre-existing
scientific story.

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:43.100 align:middle line:84%
We're writing a new
story right now.

00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:45.880 align:middle line:10%
We have to because
the evidence no longer

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:48.340 align:middle line:10%
supports the story of the past.

00:09:48.340 --> 00:09:51.040 align:middle line:84%
The evidence no longer
supports the theory

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:54.870 align:middle line:84%
that civilization, for
example, began between 5,000,

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:56.245 align:middle line:90%
5,500 years ago.

00:09:56.245 --> 00:09:57.200 align:middle line:90%
[END PLAYBACK]

