>>GEORGE: What an
exciting series on Gaia,

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:01.143 align:middle line:90%
"Ancient Civilizations."

00:10:01.143 --> 00:10:02.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LACROIX: Yeah, I'm
