00:10:12.680 --> 00:10:14.065 align:middle line:90%
what this story really was.

00:10:14.065 --> 00:10:15.440 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: Well,
it looks like you

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:19.460 align:middle line:84%
bring real science and real
metaphysics to the table,

00:10:19.460 --> 00:10:20.450 align:middle line:90%
and that's exciting.

00:10:20.450 --> 00:10:21.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LACROIX: We do.

00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:22.820 align:middle line:84%
We even go into
ice cores where we

00:10:22.820 --> 00:10:24.830 align:middle line:84%
