tsunami you just mentioned.

00:15:53.060 --> 00:15:54.330 align:middle line:90%
What do you think?

00:15:54.330 --> 00:15:55.460 align:middle line:84%
>>LACROIX: Well, that's a
really interesting thing,

00:15:55.460 --> 00:15:58.040 align:middle line:84%
