00:36:03.587 --> 00:36:05.920 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: And they never
picked back up again, did they?

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:06.837 align:middle line:90%
>>LACROIX: They don't.

00:36:06.837 --> 00:36:09.400 align:middle line:84%
In fact, every time one
of these have happened,

00:36:09.400 --> 00:36:13.090 align:middle line:84%
and according to the ancient
priests of Sais, the temple

00:36:13.090 --> 00:36:15.790 align:middle line:84%
priests and the ancient
Maya and the Aztec,

00:36:15.790 --> 00:36:19.660 align:middle line:84%
there have been at least four
to five different civilizations

00:36:19.660 --> 00:36:21.640 align:middle line:90%
that have risen up and fallen.

00:36:21.640 --> 00:36:25.150 align:middle line:84%
And every single time, we've
lost more and more knowledge

00:36:25.150 --> 00:36:27.190 align:middle line:90%
in each one of those falls.

00:36:27.190 --> 00:36:29.260 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: Matt, the great
geologist Gregg Braden,

00:36:29.260 --> 00:36:30.730 align:middle line:90%
whom we've seen--

00:36:30.730 --> 00:36:32.950 align:middle line:84%
talks about ancient
civilizations

00:36:32.950 --> 00:36:34.945 align:middle line:84%
