00:39:28.140 --> 00:39:28.380 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: Amazing.

00:39:28.380 --> 00:39:29.922 align:middle line:10%
>>LACROIX: But what's
so fascinating,

00:39:29.922 --> 00:39:32.190 align:middle line:10%
George, is that on
the Colossi of Memnon,

00:39:32.190 --> 00:39:35.520 align:middle line:10%
there is what's known as
vitrification or scarring

00:39:35.520 --> 00:39:38.340 align:middle line:10%
on one specific
part of each statue.

00:39:38.340 --> 00:39:40.860 align:middle line:84%
On the Northeast side
of each one of these

00:39:40.860 --> 00:39:44.190 align:middle line:84%
