catastrophes that

00:39:44.190 --> 00:39:47.070 align:middle line:84%
occurred that
literally were what

00:39:47.070 --> 00:39:49.470 align:middle line:84%
destroyed the civilization
that created them.

00:39:49.470 --> 00:39:51.630 align:middle line:84%
But those catastrophes
seem to have

00:39:51.630 --> 00:39:54.000 align:middle line:90%
come from a specific direction.

00:39:54.000 --> 00:39:55.530 align:middle line:84%
And what's
interesting about that

00:39:55.530 --> 00:39:58.680 align:middle line:84%
is that vitrification,
which means melting of rock,

00:39:58.680 --> 00:40:01.020 align:middle line:84%
can only occur if
temperatures in the surface

00:40:01.020 --> 00:40:03.960 align:middle line:90%
exceed 2,000 degrees.

00:40:03.960 --> 00:40:05.670 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: That's
an asteroid strike.

00:40:05.670 --> 00:40:06.915 align:middle line:84%
>>LACROIX: It's some
kind of a massive--

00:40:06.915 --> 00:40:07.170 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: Well,
where's the crater?

00:40:07.170 --> 00:40:08.878 align:middle line:10%
>>LACROIX: --heat,
either asteroid strike

